490
00:30:26,973 --> 00:30:30,573
But it isn't a question
of why you wanted it...

491
00:30:30,773 --> 00:30:32,573
...it's how you got it.

492
00:30:33,373 --> 00:30:36,873
l understand you have personal reasons
for being under stress...

493
00:30:37,073 --> 00:30:39,572
...for not acting as carefully
as you might.

494
00:30:40,272 --> 00:30:44,172
And l'm sympathetic to the way
you must feel about...

495
00:30:45,572 --> 00:30:46,572
...the Greely case.

496
00:30:46,772 --> 00:30:48,472
Greenly. Nancy Greenly.

497
00:30:48,672 --> 00:30:51,672
Greenly. Yes, Nancy Greenly case.

498
00:30:55,072 --> 00:30:58,172
l certainly don't want to lose
