1035
01:21:29,126 --> 01:21:32,926
<i>...and no clear social consensus
as to what should be done.</i>

1036
01:21:33,126 --> 01:21:37,326
<i>And the cost of care for the chronic
patient has become prohibitive.</i>

1037
01:21:37,526 --> 01:21:41,726
<i>This is particularly the case
with the long-term comatose patient.</i>

1038
01:21:41,926 --> 01:21:46,326
The Jefferson lnstitute is a government-
sponsored experimental facility...

1039
01:21:46,526 --> 01:21:50,726
...designed to provide quality
life support to the comatose patient.

1040
01:21:51,426 --> 01:21:52,826
l wish to emphasize...

1041
01:21:53,026 --> 01:21:56,626
...no moral or ethical position
is being taken here.

1042
01:21:56,926 --> 01:22:00,926
We do not participate in the debate
over whether these patients...

1043
01:22:01,126 --> 01:22:02,326
...are alive or dead...

1044
01:22:02,926 --> 01:22:06,226
...or whether their care should
be continued or terminated.

1045
01:22:06,426 --> 01:22:10,626
Society will decide if there will
be more of these facilities or not.

1046
01:22:11,226 --> 01:22:16,126
ln the meantime, we merely provide
care as inexpensively as possible.

1047
01:22:16,326 --> 01:22:18,726
Now, if you will
please come this way....

1048
01:22:19,626 --> 01:22:21,326
This is our visiting room...

1049
